name: La Rambla
description:
This serie of abstract photography are sigils for elevate the frequency connecting with the flow of Tao, through the power of colors, textures and feelings.

"Тhe gentle overcomes the rigid.
The slow overcomes the fast.
The weak overcomes the strong.

Everyone knows that the yielding overcomes the stiff,
and the soft overcomes the hard.
Yet no one applies this knowledge."

-Tao Te King
